@startuml 05-sequence-net-modes-overview

title NetMode sequence diagrams (index)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam noteFontSize 12

legend right
  Standalone
  File 05-sequence-standalone.puml
  Local GameWorld only. No IClientNetChannel.
  --
  Client
  File 05-sequence-client-remote.puml
  GameClient plus remote GameServer over LiteNetLib.
  --
  ListenServer
  File 05-sequence-listen-server.puml
  Rex.Client spawns Rex.Server then uses Client mode to localhost.
  --
  DedicatedServer
  File 05-sequence-dedicated-server.puml
  Rex.Server ServerApp loop only.
end legend

note as N1
  NetMode DedicatedServer is not started through ClientApp.Run.
  Rex.Client Program rejects that mode on the client entry point.
end note

@enduml
